data.description: Welcome to 549 Slippery Rock! This charming and spacious home is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With its open floor plan, this property boasts ample natural light throughout. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances and plenty of counter space, making it a chef's dream. The cozy living room is perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Retreat to the generous master suite, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, accommodating all your needs. Step outside to the beautifully landscaped backyard, ideal for outdoor activities and gatherings. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers, this home is a true gem. Don't miss the opportunity to make 549 Slippery Rock your new home!
